post.description:
Aggregate and calculate incident data under the entire account:
- If aggregate_unit is set, further split and display by unit;
- If split_hours is set, further split and display by time period;
- If neither is set, only return one aggregated data.

Aggregate and calculate incident data by team:
- If aggregate_unit is set, further split and display by unit;
- If split_hours is set, further split and display by time period;
- If neither is set, only split and display by team.

Aggregate and calculate incident data by channel:
- If aggregate_unit is set, further split and display by unit;
- If split_hours is set, further split and display by time period;
- If neither is set, only split and display by channel.

Aggregate and calculate incident data by person:
- If aggregate_unit is set, further split and display by unit;
- If split_hours is set, further split and display by time period;
- If neither is set, only split and display by person.

